quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,15,“Ndipo adaika panthaka mapiri ataliatali kuti (nthaka) isagwedezeke nanu; ndipo (adaika) mitsinje ndi misewu kuti muongoke (potsata njira yeniyeni ndikukafika komwe mukufuna)
  16,16,"“Ndipo (adaikanso) zizindikiro zina, ndiponso kupyolera m’nyenyezi, iwo amalondola njira"
  16,17,“Kodi Yemwe amalenga angalingane ndi omwe salenga? Kodi simungakumbukire (ndikudziwa kulakwa kwanu pomuyerekeza Allah ndi mafano)
  16,18,"“Ngati mutayesera kuwerengera mtendere wa Allah simungathe kuuwerengera (wonse); ndithudi, Allah Ngokhululuka kwambiri, Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  16,19,"“Ndipo Allah akuzidziwa zimene mukuzibisa, ndi zomwe mukuwonetsera"
  16,20,"“Ndipo zomwe mukuzipembedza kusiya Allah, sizilenga chilichonse, ndipo izo nzolengedwa"
  16,21,“Zakufa zopanda moyo; ndipo sizizindikira kuti nliti akufa adzaukitsidwa (m’manda mwawo)
  16,22,"“Mulungu wanu ndi Mulungu Mmodzi Yekha; koma amene sakhulupirira za tsiku la chimaliziro, mitima yawo ikukana (kukhulupirira umodzi wa Allah), ndipo iwo akudzitukumula"
  16,23,"“Palibe chikaiko, Allah akudziwa zomwe akubisa, ndi zomwe akuzilengeza. Ndithudi, Iye sakonda odzikuza"
  16,24,"“Ndipo (osakhulupirira) akafunsidwa: “Kodi Mbuye wanu watumizanji (kwa Mneneri Muhammad {s.a.w})?” Akunena: “(Sadatumize chilichonse koma) nthano zabodza za anthu akale.”"
  16,25,"“(Motero akuwasokeretsa anthu) kuti akasenze mitolo yawo (ya machimo) yokwanira pa tsiku la Qiyâma, ndiponso gawo lamitolo ya omwe akuwasokeretsa popanda kuzindikira (osokerawo). Tamverani! Ndi yoipa kwabasi mitolo yomwe azikaisenza"
  16,26,“Adachita ndale omwe adalipo patsogolo pawo; choncho Allah adagumula maziko anyumba zawo. Ndipo madenga adawagwera pamwamba pawo; ndipo chilango chidawadzera kuchokera komwe sadali kukudziwa